creator: Skyscanner Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Get inspiration, and plan and book flights, hotels and transport – we're here to make it all super easy, wherever you are. Join 90+ million others who use us to find the best flight prices and amazing hotel discounts. Here, you can explore everything the travel industry has to offer. And there are no booking fees or hidden charges – just the best prices.

* BOOK YOUR WHOLE TRIP
Yep, you can. Get where you want to go, stay where you want to stay, and get loads of suggestions on what to do while you’re there – based on other travellers’ reviews.

* FIND THE BEST VALUE FLIGHTS
Search and compare hundreds of flights all in one place, from every major airline, including British Airways, easyJet, Emirates and Singapore Airlines. Find the cheapest months and dates to fly, using our colour-coded calendar and chart views when you enter your travel dates. Not yet ready to book? Set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when it changes.

* GET THE RIGHT ROOM
Thought we were just about flights? Nope, we’ve got your stay covered too. Compare great deals from thousands of hotels, resorts, apartments and hostels from providers like Booking.com and Expedia, all in one place. Or find rooms near your current location and grab a last-minute deal.

* RENT A CAR
Choose where and when to pick up your car rental, and we’ll show you the deals. You can filter your search by vehicle type, fuel type and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will make sure you’re not paying too much on fuel – we’ve got your back.

* NO ADDED FEES, EVER
Did we mention that we don’t charge any booking fees? Never. None at all.

* COMPARE HOTELS WITH EASE
We pull a comprehensive list of hotel amenities and real traveler reviews for every hotel we find, making your search easy. If Expedia is showing the lowest price for a double room, you’ll know. If Trip.com is offering the best refundable room rate, we’ll show!


* FIND INSPIRATION
Itching to travel but no idea where to go? We’ve got you. Tap ‘Explore’ to check out our inspirational destinations with the best deals. And read reviews from other like-minded travelers so you know you won’t be disappointed.


* CUSTOMISE YOUR SEARCH
British Airways or easyJet? Singapore Airlines or AirAsia? Filter your flight search by flight duration, airline, number of stops, travel class, departure and arrival times. Easy.


* RELIABLE AIRLINE RATINGS
From easyJet’s customer service to Emirates’ ease of booking, and from British Airways’ pricing, to Singapore Airlines’ overall booking experience, our Partner Quality Score allows you to see how all the big airlines are rated by other travellers. Things like customer service, ease of booking and accurate pricing are all scored and available for you to see before you book.

* SAVE YOUR FLIGHTS
Want to look, but not ready to book? No problem. We have a ‘saved flights’ setting where you can ‘star’ a flight you like. Then it’ll show up on your home screen, so you can pick up where you left off.

* GET PRICE ALERTS
Found that ideal flight to visit friends, or maybe that romantic room in Barcelona via Expedia, but you’re just not ready to book? Set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when rates rise or fall, so you can buy when the price is right.

* BROWSE BACK THROUGH RECENT SEARCHES
Your recent flight and hotel searches will be right there on your home screen when you next open the app.

Ready? Enjoy!

Price Prediction is now out and will help you get the best travel deal possible. Choose your flights and we’ll suggest whether to book now or later.
So, if we think you should hold out for a better deal, we’ll let you know.
Based on years of flight data, it’s just launched exclusively on our app.

container.value:

Edinburgh EH3 9EN.
United Kingdom

creator: Skyscanner Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Get inspiration, and plan and book flights, hotels and transport – we're here to make it all super easy, wherever you are. Join 90+ million others who use us to find the best flight prices and amazing hotel discounts. Here, you can explore everything the travel industry has to offer. And there are no booking fees or hidden charges – just the best prices.

* BOOK YOUR WHOLE TRIP
Yep, you can. Get where you want to go, stay where you want to stay, and get loads of suggestions on what to do while you’re there – based on other travellers’ reviews.

* FIND THE BEST VALUE FLIGHTS
Search and compare hundreds of flights all in one place, from every major airline, including British Airways, easyJet, Emirates and Singapore Airlines. Find the cheapest months and dates to fly, using our colour-coded calendar and chart views when you enter your travel dates. Not yet ready to book? Set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when it changes.

* GET THE RIGHT ROOM
Thought we were just about flights? Nope, we’ve got your stay covered too. Compare great deals from thousands of hotels, resorts, apartments and hostels from providers like Booking.com and Expedia, all in one place. Or find rooms near your current location and grab a last-minute deal.

* RENT A CAR
Choose where and when to pick up your car rental, and we’ll show you the deals. You can filter your search by vehicle type, fuel type and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will make sure you’re not paying too much on fuel – we’ve got your back.

* NO ADDED FEES, EVER
Did we mention that we don’t charge any booking fees? Never. None at all.

* COMPARE HOTELS WITH EASE
We pull a comprehensive list of hotel amenities and real traveler reviews for every hotel we find, making your search easy. If Expedia is showing the lowest price for a double room, you’ll know. If Trip.com is offering the best refundable room rate, we’ll show!


* FIND INSPIRATION
Itching to travel but no idea where to go? We’ve got you. Tap ‘Explore’ to check out our inspirational destinations with the best deals. And read reviews from other like-minded travelers so you know you won’t be disappointed.


* CUSTOMISE YOUR SEARCH
British Airways or easyJet? Singapore Airlines or AirAsia? Filter your flight search by flight duration, airline, number of stops, travel class, departure and arrival times. Easy.


* RELIABLE AIRLINE RATINGS
From easyJet’s customer service to Emirates’ ease of booking, and from British Airways’ pricing, to Singapore Airlines’ overall booking experience, our Partner Quality Score allows you to see how all the big airlines are rated by other travellers. Things like customer service, ease of booking and accurate pricing are all scored and available for you to see before you book.

* SAVE YOUR FLIGHTS
Want to look, but not ready to book? No problem. We have a ‘saved flights’ setting where you can ‘star’ a flight you like. Then it’ll show up on your home screen, so you can pick up where you left off.

* GET PRICE ALERTS
Found that ideal flight to visit friends, or maybe that romantic room in Barcelona via Expedia, but you’re just not ready to book? Set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when rates rise or fall, so you can buy when the price is right.

* BROWSE BACK THROUGH RECENT SEARCHES
Your recent flight and hotel searches will be right there on your home screen when you next open the app.

Ready? Enjoy!

Get inspiration, and plan and book your whole trip - we're here to make it all super easy, wherever you are. Join 90+ million others who use us to find the best flight prices and amazing hotel discounts. Here, you can explore everything the travel industry has to offer. And there are no booking fees or hidden charges - just the best prices.

* BOOK YOUR WHOLE TRIP


Yep, you can. Get where you want to go, stay where you want to stay, and get loads of suggestions on what to do while you're there - based on other travellers' reviews.

* FIND THE BEST VALUE FLIGHTS


Search and compare hundreds of flights all in one place to find the great prices available. Not ready to book yet? Set up a Price Alert and we'll let you know when it changes.

* GET THE RIGHT HOTEL


Thought we were just about flights? Nope, we've got your stay covered too. Compare great deals from thousands of hotels, resorts, apartments and hostels all over the world. Or find rooms near your current location and grab a last-minute deal.

* RENT A CAR


Choose where and when to pick up your car rental, and we'll show you the deals. You can filter your search by vehicle type, fuel type and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will make sure you're not paying too much on fuel - we've got your back.

* NO ADDED FEES EVER


Did we mention we don't charge any booking fees? Never. None at all.

* FIND INSPIRATION


Itching to travel but no idea where to go? We've got you. Tap 'Explore' to check out our inspirational destinations with the best deals.

* CUSTOMISE YOUR SEARCH


Know what you're looking for? Filter your flight search by flight duration, airline, number of stops, travel class, departure and arrival times. Easy.

* FIND THE GREENEST FLIGHTS


We're committed to lead the global transformation to modern, sustainable travel. Our first step is introducing the 'Greener choices' label to our platform, helping you lessen the environmental impact of travel by choosing flights which emit less CO2.

* SAVE YOUR FLIGHTS


Want to look but not ready to book? No problem. We have a 'saved flights' setting where you can 'star' a flight you like. Then it'll show up on your home screen, so you can pick up where you left off.

Enjoy!

creator: Skyscanner Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Skyscanner makes planning your next trip easy.
No matter where you are - search for flights, hotels and car hire deals to anywhere in the world, on the move. Save time and money by comparing and booking from your favourite travel brands all in one place too. There are no booking fees or hidden charges – just the best prices. Here’s how to use our app:

Find inspiration
Can’t decide where? Excellent. Start by exploring everywhere first. Tap ‘Everywhere’ in our search bar to find cheap flights literally anywhere around the world and get ideas for your next holiday.

Filter your search
Know what you’re looking for? Use our smart filters to search by flight duration, airline, number of stops, travel class, departure and arrival times. Easy.

Our travel map
We get it, things are always changing. Before or after booking, check out our handy travel map so you can stay up to date with the latest restrictions and entry requirements for wherever in the world you’re off to next. Less travel stress, more holiday fun!

The best time to fly
You’ve chosen where it will be, now to find the best dates to book your holiday. Our calendar view breaks down the cheapest dates in a chosen month so you can find the right flight deal. Not ready to book yet? Set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when the flight price changes so you’re always booking at the right time.

The right hotel at the right price
Thought we were just about cheap flights? Nope, we’ve got your stay covered too. Compare and book cheap deals from thousands of hotels, resorts, apartments, motels and hostels all over the world. Or find rooms near your current location and grab a last-minute deal for your next holiday.

Hire a car
Choose where and when to pick up your car hire, and we’ll show you cheap prices and deals. You can filter your search by vehicle type, fuel type and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will make sure you’re not paying too much on fuel – we’ve got your back.

Book with who you trust
Compare all your top travel brands in one place - Easyjet, Ryanair, British Airways, American Airlines, Wizz Air, Expedia, Booking.com, lastminute.com and more. Plus, get recent reviews on our travel partners from our community of travellers.

No added fees ever
Did we mention we don’t charge any booking fees? Never. None at all.

Find the greenest flights
Lessen your environmental impact by booking flights that emit less CO2. We make these flights easy to find with our ‘Greener choices’ label when you’re searching for that next trip.

Save your flights
Want to look but not ready to book? No problem. We have a ‘saved’ feature where you can ‘heart’ flights or hotels you like. Then it’ll show up on your trips, so you can pick up where you left off and get booking.

Why Skyscanner?
• The Telegraph; “The only 20 travel apps you’ll ever need”
• The New York Times; “Apps for Travelers Dreaming of Their Next Trip”
• Elite Daily; “7 holiday travel apps that’ll let you jingle around the world’
• Pocket-lint; “4 apps to get you ready for summer”

Let’s get social
• Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/skyscanner
• Instagram: @skyscanner
• Twitter: @skyscanner
• LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/skyscanner/
• Website: www.skyscanner.net

creator: Skyscanner Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Get inspiration, and plan and book your whole trip—we're here to make it all super easy, wherever you are. Join 90+ million others who use us to find the best flight prices and awesome hotel discounts. Here, you can explore everything the travel industry has to offer. And there are no booking fees or hidden charges—just the best prices.

* BOOK YOUR WHOLE TRIP
Yes, you can. Get where you want to go, stay where you want to stay, and get lots of suggestions on what to do while you’re there—based on other travelers’ reviews.

* FIND THE BEST VALUE FLIGHTS
Search and compare hundreds of flights all in one place. Find the cheapest months and dates to fly, using our color-coded calendar and chart views when you enter your travel dates. Not ready to book right now? Set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when it changes.

* GET THE RIGHT HOTEL
Thought we were just about flights? Nope, we’ve got your stay covered too. Compare great deals from thousands of hotels, resorts, apartments, and hostels all over the world. Or, find rooms near your current location and grab a last-minute deal.

* RENT A CAR
Choose where and when to pick up your car rental, and we’ll show you the deals. You can filter your search by vehicle type, fuel type, and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will make sure that you’re not paying too much for fuel—we’ve got your back.

* NO ADDED FEES, EVER
Did we mention that we don’t charge any booking fees? Never. None at all.

* FIND INSPIRATION
Itching to travel, but no idea where to go? We’ve got you covered. Tap “Explore” to check out our inspirational destinations with the best deals. And read reviews from other like-minded travelers so that you know you won’t be disappointed.

* CUSTOMIZE YOUR SEARCH
Know what you’re looking for? Filter your flight search by flight duration, airline, number of stops, travel class, departure times, and arrival times. Easy.

* SAVE YOUR FLIGHTS
Want to look, but not ready to book? No problem. We have a “saved flights” setting that allows you to “star” a flight you like. Then it’ll show up on your home screen, so you can pick up where you left off.

* BROWSE RECENT SEARCHES
Pick up where you left off. Your recent travel searches will be right there on your home screen when you next open the app.

Enjoy!

descriptionHtml:
Skyscanner makes planning your next trip easy.
No matter where you are - search for flights, hotels and car hire deals to anywhere in the world, on the move. Save time and money by comparing and booking from your favourite travel brands like Ryanair, easyJet, British Airways all in one place too. There are no booking fees or hidden charges – just the best prices. Here’s how to use our app:

Find inspiration
Can’t decide where? Excellent. Start by exploring everywhere first. Tap ‘Everywhere’ in our search bar to find cheap flights literally anywhere around the world and get ideas for your next holiday.

Filter your search
Know what you’re looking for? Use our smart filters to search by flight duration, airline, number of stops, travel class, departure and arrival times.

The best time to fly
You’ve chosen where it will be, now to find the best dates to book your holiday. Our calendar view breaks down the cheapest dates in a chosen month so you can find the right flight deal. Not ready to book yet? Set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when the flight price changes so you’re always booking at the right time.

The right hotel at the right price
Thought we were just about cheap flights? Nope, we’ve got your stay covered too. Compare and book cheap deals from thousands of hotels, resorts, apartments, motels and hostels all over the world. Or find rooms near your current location and grab a last-minute deal for your next holiday.

Hire a car
Choose where and when to pick up your car hire, and we’ll show you cheap prices and deals. You can filter your search by vehicle type, fuel type and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will make sure you’re not paying too much on fuel – we’ve got your back.

Book with who you trust
Compare all your top travel brands in one place - Easyjet, Ryanair, British Airways, American Airlines, Wizz Air, Expedia, Booking.com, lastminute.com and more. Plus, get recent reviews on our travel partners from our community of travellers.

No added fees ever
Did we mention we don’t charge any booking fees? Never. None at all.

Save your flights
Want to look but not ready to book? No problem. We have a ‘saved’ feature where you can ‘heart’ flights or hotels you like. Then it’ll show up on your trips, so you can pick up where you left off and get booking.

Why Skyscanner?
• The Telegraph; “The only 20 travel apps you’ll ever need”
• The New York Times; “Apps for Travelers Dreaming of Their Next Trip”
• Elite Daily; “7 holiday travel apps that’ll let you jingle around the world’
• Pocket-lint; “4 apps to get you ready for summer”

Let’s get social
• Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/skyscanner
• Instagram: @skyscanner
• Twitter: @skyscanner
• LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/skyscanner/
• Website: www.skyscanner.net
descriptionShort: The travel app that makes booking cheap flights, hotels & car hire easy.

descriptionHtml:
Skyscanner makes planning your next trip easy
No matter where you are – search for cheap flights, hotels and car rental deals to anywhere in the world, on the move. Save time and money by comparing deals and booking trips with top travel brands like Booking.com, easyJet, and British Airways all in one place. There are no booking fees or hidden charges – just wonderfully cheap prices.

If you’re ready to use Skyscanner for your next trip, here’s how:

Find vacation inspiration
If you can’t decide where to go, why not explore everywhere? Tap “Everywhere” in our search bar to find cheap flights literally anywhere around the world and get ideas for your next vacation.

Filter your search
If you know what kind of travel information you’re looking for, use our smart filters to search by flight duration, airline, number of stops, travel class, plus departure and arrival times. Planning your vacation has never felt so efficient.

Fly at the best time
You’ve chosen your destination, now you need to find the best dates for those cheap flights. Enter Skyscanner calendar view, which breaks down the cheapest dates in your chosen month. If you’re not ready to book your trip, you can set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when the flight price changes, so you’re always booking at the right time.

Find the cheapest month to fly
If you don’t know which month to take your trip, you can easily find the cheapest month to fly to a certain destination. Just tap “Search Anytime” when selecting your dates and we’ll show you the cheapest price available for flights in each month over the next year.

Compare hotels
We’re not just about cheap flights – we’ve got your hotel stay covered too. In fact, you can compare and book cheap deals from thousands of hotels, resorts, apartments, motels and hostels around the globe for your next vacation. Or, find rooms near your current location and grab a last-minute deal.

Rent a car
Choose where and when to pick up your car rental, and we’ll show you cheap prices and car hire deals. You can compare with ease by filtering your search by vehicle type, fuel type and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will help you keep fuel costs down.

Book with who you trust
Compare all your top travel brands in one place before booking your vacation – Booking.com, easyJet, British Airways, Wizz Air, Jet2, Expedia, Trip.com, Turkish Airlines, United Airlines, Agoda and more. Plus, get recent reviews on Skyscanner travel partners from our community of travellers.

Link up travel plans
Vacations, work trips, family events – travelling can be a social affair, so we make it easy to coordinate plans. Simply tap the share icon on any flight or hotel information to forward it to your travel pals. You can even share flight search results for a route, or booking details for an itinerary.

Save flights and hotels for later
If a flight or hotel has caught your eye, just tap the heart icon, and they will save to your Skyscanner profile. You can then browse other deals, safe in the knowledge that we’ll notify you if your saved flight price changes.

No added fees, ever
Did we mention we don’t charge any booking fees? Never. None at all.

creator: Skyscanner Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Skyscanner makes planning your next trip easy
No matter where you are – search for cheap flights, hotels and car rental deals to anywhere in the world, on the move. Save time and money by comparing deals and booking trips with top travel brands like Booking.com, easyJet, and British Airways all in one place. There are no booking fees or hidden charges – just wonderfully cheap prices.

If you’re ready to use Skyscanner for your next trip, here’s how:

Find vacation inspiration
If you can’t decide where to go, why not explore everywhere? Tap “Everywhere” in our search bar to find cheap flights literally anywhere around the world and get ideas for your next vacation.

Filter your search
If you know what kind of travel information you’re looking for, use our smart filters to search by flight duration, airline, number of stops, travel class, plus departure and arrival times. Planning your vacation has never felt so efficient.

Fly at the best time
You’ve chosen your destination, now you need to find the best dates for those cheap flights. Enter Skyscanner calendar view, which breaks down the cheapest dates in your chosen month. If you’re not ready to book your trip, you can set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when the flight price changes, so you’re always booking at the right time.

Find the cheapest month to fly
If you don’t know which month to take your trip, you can easily find the cheapest month to fly to a certain destination. Just tap “Search Anytime” when selecting your dates and we’ll show you the cheapest price available for flights in each month over the next year.

Compare hotels
We’re not just about cheap flights – we’ve got your hotel stay covered too. In fact, you can compare and book cheap deals from thousands of hotels, resorts, apartments, motels and hostels around the globe for your next vacation. Or, find rooms near your current location and grab a last-minute deal.

Rent a car
Choose where and when to pick up your car rental, and we’ll show you cheap prices and car hire deals. You can compare with ease by filtering your search by vehicle type, fuel type and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will help you keep fuel costs down.

Book with who you trust
Compare all your top travel brands in one place before booking your vacation – Booking.com, easyJet, British Airways, Wizz Air, Jet2, Expedia, Trip.com, Turkish Airlines, United Airlines, Agoda and more. Plus, get recent reviews on Skyscanner travel partners from our community of travellers.

Link up travel plans
Vacations, work trips, family events – travelling can be a social affair, so we make it easy to coordinate plans. Simply tap the share icon on any flight or hotel information to forward it to your travel pals. You can even share flight search results for a route, or booking details for an itinerary.

Save flights and hotels for later
If a flight or hotel has caught your eye, just tap the heart icon, and they will save to your Skyscanner profile. You can then browse other deals, safe in the knowledge that we’ll notify you if your saved flight price changes.

No added fees, ever
Did we mention we don’t charge any booking fees? Never. None at all.

Save time and money by comparing deals and booking trips with top travel brands like Booking.com, easyJet, and British Airways all in one place. There are no booking fees or hidden charges – just wonderfully cheap prices.

If you’re ready to use Skyscanner for your next trip, here’s how:

Find vacation inspiration
If you can’t decide where to go, why not explore everywhere? Tap “Everywhere” in our search bar to find cheap flights literally anywhere around the world and get ideas for your next vacation.

Filter your search
If you know what kind of travel information you’re looking for, use our smart filters to search by flight duration, airline, number of stops, travel class, plus departure and arrival times. Planning your vacation has never felt so efficient.

Fly at the best time
You’ve chosen your destination, now you need to find the best dates for those cheap flights. Enter Skyscanner calendar view, which breaks down the cheapest dates in your chosen month. If you’re not ready to book your trip, you can set up a Price Alert and we’ll let you know when the flight price changes, so you’re always booking at the right time.

Find the cheapest month to fly
If you don’t know which month to take your trip, you can easily find the cheapest month to fly to a certain destination. Just tap “Search Anytime” when selecting your dates and we’ll show you the cheapest price available for flights in each month over the next year.

Compare hotels
We’re not just about cheap flights – we’ve got your hotel stay covered too. In fact, you can compare and book cheap deals from thousands of hotels, resorts, apartments, motels and hostels around the globe for your next vacation. Or, find rooms near your current location and grab a last-minute deal.

Rent a car
Choose where and when to pick up your car rental, and we’ll show you cheap prices and car hire deals. You can compare with ease by filtering your search by vehicle type, fuel type and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will help you keep fuel costs down.

Book with who you trust
Compare all your top travel brands in one place before booking your vacation – Booking.com, easyJet, British Airways, Wizz Air, Jet2, Expedia, Trip.com, Turkish Airlines, United Airlines, Agoda and more. Plus, get recent reviews on Skyscanner travel partners from our community of travellers.

Link up travel plans
Vacations, work trips, family events – travelling can be a social affair, so we make it easy to coordinate plans. Simply tap the share icon on any flight or hotel information to forward it to your travel pals. You can even share flight search results for a route, or booking details for an itinerary.

Save flights and hotels for later
If a flight or hotel has caught your eye, just tap the heart icon, and they will save to your Skyscanner profile. You can then browse other deals, safe in the knowledge that we’ll notify you if your saved flight price changes.

No added fees, ever
Did we mention we don’t charge any booking fees? Never. None at all.

Hire a car
Choose where and when to pick up your car hire, and we’ll show you affordable options from top car hire agencies, including Hertz, Avis, Enterprise and Europcar . You can filter your search by vehicle type, fuel type and features. And our Fair Fuel Policy flag will make sure you’re not paying too much on fuel – we’ve got your back.

Book with who you trust
Compare all your top travel brands, including online travel agencies (OTA), in one place - easyJet, Ryanair, British Airways, Lufthansa, Wizz Air, Expedia, Booking.com, lastminute.com and more. Plus, get recent reviews on our travel partners from our community of travellers.

No added fees ever
Did we mention we don’t charge any booking fees? Never. None at all. Book directly with airlines, hotels, and travel services with total transparency.

Save your flights
Want to look but not ready to book? No problem. We have a ‘saved’ feature where you can ‘heart’ flights or hotels you like. Then it’ll show up on your trips, so you can pick up where you left off and get booking.
